lead_paragraph: The walkout by home fans in the 77th minute over rising ticket prices is no excuse for Liverpool's 2-2 Premier League draw with Sunderland on Saturday, captain Jordan Henderson has said.

headline.print_headline: Fans Walkout No Excuse for Liverpool, Says Henderson
headline.main: Fans Walkout No Excuse for Liverpool, Says Henderson
